videos.description: Obi Toppin sets a screen and rolls to the hoop, rising above the rim to catch Jalen Crutcher's lob and throw down the alley-oop.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Toppin flushes alley-oop for Dayton) 2020/02/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Toppin flushes alley-oop for Dayton

videos.description: George Mason guard Xavier Johnson's shot is off the mark, but AJ Wilson crashes the offensive glass and uses just one hand to flush the putback slam.

videos.headline: Wilson flies in for 1-handed putback jam

videos.description: Dayton pushes the pace in transition and Obi Toppin banks home the shot in traffic despite being fouled.
